{
  "stem": "11723.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "And he was so emaciated that when my father's brother brought a loaf of bread, the two of them fought over it.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "My grandfather was like an animal.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "He was just so emaciated, so hungry, he would kill for that bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "And I understand from what he could describe to us, that he was living under terrible circumstances in the slave labor camp and had a very cruel officer.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "And several times, they hung him up with-- upside down with-- by his feet and left him there all night.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "And some nights, they made him sit up somewhere high and make sounds like a rooster all night.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "And they beat him very, very frequently, and he got a hemorrhage.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And that's when he lost the power of speech.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "But he came back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "So he was the first one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "Then one day, we were living at the old apartment-- the same place where we lived before the war.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 91,
      "text": "And I was playing in front of the apartment, and my mother's younger brother came into the courtyard.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 92,
      "text": "He also came back from slave labor camp.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 93,
      "text": "Now he was only 23 years old and he had typhoid fever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 94,
      "text": "And he saw me up on the-- I don't know if you've ever seen how the apartment buildings are built in Europe.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 95,
      "text": "They have an inner corridor around a courtyard.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 96,
      "text": "He saw me on the inner corridor, and he yelled up to me, and he collapsed.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 97,
      "text": "And was-- he almost died of the typhoid fever that he had, but he recovered.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 98,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then my aunt-- my other uncle came back from-- my mother's older brother.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 99,
      "text": "And his wife-- the one who was in the ghetto with my grandmother first-- she survived with my two cousins.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
